<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <title>Bumblebee Foundation</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .main-container {
            display: flex;
            width: 150%;
            height: 100vh;
            margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%); 
            margin-right: calc(-25vw + 25%); 
            
            overflow: hidden;

        }

       
        #hero {
            flex: 1;  
            height: 100vh;
            background-image: url('/Images/funding.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;

        }

        .overlay {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .overlay h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            animation: fadeIn 5s ease-in-out;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        @@keyframes fadeIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }

            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        #hero:hover .overlay {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
        }

       
        #about {
            flex: 1;  
            height: 100vh;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            margin: 0;
        }

        #about:hover {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        #about img {
            max-width: 250px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        #about .text {
            max-width: 600px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        #about h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #388e3c;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-left: 5px solid #388e3c;
            padding-left: 15px;
            animation: slideIn 1s ease-out;
        }

        #about p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #666;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        #about p:hover {
            color: #333;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background-color: #388e3c;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(56, 142, 60, 0.3);
            transition: background-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #2c7030;
            box-shadow: 0px 6px 12px rgba(56, 142, 60, 0.5);
        }

        @@keyframes slideIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-30px);
            }

            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        @@media (max-width: 800px) {
            .main-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                height: auto;
            }

            #hero, #about {
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                min-height: 100vh;
            }

            #hero .overlay h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            #about {
                align-items: center;
            }

            #about img {
                max-width: 200px;
            }

            #about h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            #about .text {
                max-width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="main-container">
        
        <section id="hero">
            <div class="overlay">
                <h1>Welcome to Bumblebee Foundation</h1>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="about">
            <img src="/Images/logo.png" alt="Bumblebee Foundation Logo">
            <div class="text">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>
                    The Bumblebee Foundation connects offshore sponsors with South African non-profits, amplifying impact and empowering communities to tackle social and environmental challenges.
                    Committed to transparency, accountability, and sustainability, we maximize donation effectiveness and ensure resources support long-term solutions.
                    Through collaboration, we strive to create a more equitable and resilient future for all.
                </p>
                <a href="/Home/AboutUs" class="cta-button">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
